{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "纳姆（和服Ver.） 第4话 内心真正的恐惧",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不要……不要说了……\\n求你了！不要再说了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我明明想要忘记这件事！\\n一直不去思考这件事！\\n不要对我提起这件事啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "呜呜……呜呜呜……\\n呜呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "怎……怎么回事！？\\n纳姆颤抖着蜷缩在地……\\n不好！晴、晴明大人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "我知道，不要晃我，葛叶。\\n看来……她内心的恐惧\\n比想象中还要更加深刻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "术式的效果太强，\\n她已经完全丧失斗志了。\\n这下有点麻烦……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "诶！不、不得了！\\n晴明大人快想想办法帮她呀！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "我们帮不到她。\\n术式在恐惧成形之时就已经发动，\\n要消除也只能靠她自己。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "怎、怎么会这样……\\n纳姆，你能听到吗！？\\n加油……不要输给自己啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "呜呜……就、就算你这样说。\\n我也办不到啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我只是……一直都对\\n这份“恐惧”视而不见，\\n它却从未从心中消失过啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "没错，\\n无论尤蒂尔和塞西娅有多长寿，\\n在精灵面前也不过是弹指一瞬。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "我只能孤身一人\\n看着大家一个个离我而去。\\n这就是身为不同种族的我的命运。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "呜呜……没错，没错的。\\n这就是现实。无论再怎么努力，\\n也没法改变这现实……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "这可不好说。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "的确，你是会被留下来的一方。\\n你的恐惧我也能感同身受。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "因为……我曾经也为\\n同样的恐惧而苦恼过。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "晴明……你也？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "嗯。我的外公是前一任丑之龙氏。\\n从我记事起，就已经大致\\n知道他将要离去的时日了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "只是后来因为道满那混蛋，\\n事态变得十分混乱。\\n这个我们暂且不谈。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "即便是这样，我也克服了恐惧\\n并继承了龙氏之名了结了恩怨……\\n如今才能站在这里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "想要彻底消除对未来的恐惧\\n恐怕很难。但是有能够克服\\n这种恐惧的方法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "那就是与你心中所想之人\\n一同创造很多美好的回忆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "很多……美好的回忆……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "没错。我和我所尊敬的外公之间\\n有很多很多快乐的回忆。\\n像是一同庆祝新年这样的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "嗯嗯。所以晴明大人也常说\\n希望大家度过一个愉快的新年\\n而每次都……啊好疼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "不要说废话。不过……\\n回忆确实能够给人\\n面对未来的勇气。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "所以，如果你害怕未来，\\n那就创造足以克服\\n这份恐惧的美好回忆吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "只要明白了这点，\\n你就不会再败给这份恐惧了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "晴明……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "只是，过于执着于回忆，\\n也有可能会让你变成\\n被过去所束缚的蠢货……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "但我认为，\\n如果能够正确克服恐惧，\\n回忆就能成为面对未来的希望。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "那个……晴明。\\n我能问你一件事吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "什么事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "你送走外公后所找到的\\n如今的希望……是什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "是成为像外公那样伟大的阴阳师。\\n成为一位值得葛叶和牛头天王\\n追随的主人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110375_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "晴明",
            "context": "以及，将外公传承给我的，\\n再传承给他们……\\n让这份回忆继续延续下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n和外公之间的回忆成为了你的希望啊。\\n谢谢你告诉我这些。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "多亏了你，我稍微有一点勇气了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "为什么……\\n为什么要站起来？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "还用问吗，\\n当然是要赶快完成这试炼，\\n和大家一起过个开心的新年啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "然后一同创造很多很多美好的回忆。\\n所以……我可没时间\\n因为这点事就气馁呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "我不明白。\\n即使你这么说，\\n你的脸上却还写着恐惧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "可你又为什么……\\n能够站起来呢！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "因为我喜欢\\n和大家一起度过的时光。\\n因为我知道那时光之中有我的希望。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "所以我一定能够面对未来，\\n我一定不会再败给自己的“恐惧”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "即使你就是我自己，\\n我也不会对打扰我创造美好回忆的家伙\\n手下留情的！嘿呀——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "呀啊啊……\\n这是……\\n顽强而又勇敢的心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "第三项试炼",
            "context": "这就是我的……希望……\\n有了它，我一定也……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊……消、消失了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "也就是说！\\n我完成了试炼！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "太好啦！通过了通过了！\\n真的……真的是太好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110374_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "葛叶",
            "context": "完成三项试炼，\\n任务终于完成啦。\\n快看！地面开始……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "太好啦！地面开始发光，\\n题目上浮现出印章了！\\n这下……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呼……终于走到这里了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊，尤蒂尔！\\n大家也都来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "纳姆！\\n太好了，总算追上你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊！我看看，这一格的任务是……\\n呃，怎么是全体STOP啊！\\n咦？不过似乎已经完成了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "也就是说，是纳姆完成了任务？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊，嗯。\\n刚刚勉强通过了啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊。\\n想必是挺困难的试炼吧……\\n纳姆，你真厉害！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶、诶嘿嘿。我可努力了！\\n而且……多亏有人给了我建议♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嚯，有人给建议啊。\\n谁啊？\\n葛叶……还是说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶嘿嘿，保密～\\n要是我说了，\\n那人肯定会害羞的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不说这个了，我们赶快前进吧！\\n现在和大家成功会合，\\n让我感觉特别有干劲呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "感觉现在无论什么题目\\n都难不倒我呢！诶嘿嘿♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}